    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/j0rgbv-09/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_PRODUCT&editorId=608890156795036215&sectionId=609014864995681134)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1zHPMhpBz_text","label":"gg1zHPMhpBz_text","default":"<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Used by Over 73,000 Men</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkpSrCi-A9_text","label":"ggkpSrCi-A9_text","default":"<p>“Finally something that doesn’t make me look like a carrot. Looks like I spent a weekend at the beach.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNVSHeW7MC_text","label":"ggNVSHeW7MC_text","default":"<p><strong>— Mark R.</strong>, 38, verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTRcDmfbFD_text","label":"ggTRcDmfbFD_text","default":"<p>“My wife thought I’d been golfing all weekend. I didn’t correct her.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4y4VREaCC_text","label":"gg4y4VREaCC_text","default":"<p><strong>— Joe M.</strong>, 54, verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbhSAwLTAV_text","label":"ggbhSAwLTAV_text","default":"<p>“Been using it six months. No one’s ever figured out it’s fake. That’s the only review that matters.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg57LsH2zqk_text","label":"gg57LsH2zqk_text","default":"<p><strong>— Andrew T.</strong>, 47, verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrQd1iPxbw_text","label":"ggrQd1iPxbw_text","default":"<p>“Tried other self-tanners. All of them turned me orange or blotchy. This one doesn’t. Finally.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbj4Dq2Q8J_text","label":"ggbj4Dq2Q8J_text","default":"<p><strong>— Luke B.</strong>, 35, verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtjvmHBq8W_text","label":"ggtjvmHBq8W_text","default":"<p>“I hate sitting in the sun but I was pale as hell. Now I’ve got color year-round. Stupid easy to use.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUPmefj8Qs_text","label":"ggUPmefj8Qs_text","default":"<p><strong>— Dave S.</strong>, 42, verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggF68nvbIcr_text","label":"ggF68nvbIcr_text","default":"<p>“No streaks. No patches. No fake look. Three drops. Two minutes. Done. Perfect if you don’t have time for nonsense.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCUqqk9eUR_text","label":"ggCUqqk9eUR_text","default":"<p><strong>— Frank L.</strong>, 33, verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoN41NO0dB_text","label":"ggoN41NO0dB_text","default":"<p>“At my brother’s wedding people kept asking where I went on vacation. I was home the whole time.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoZwto1HxO_text","label":"ggoZwto1HxO_text","default":"<p><strong>— Paul C.</strong>, 51, verified buyer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnmQExruP-_text","label":"ggnmQExruP-_text","default":"<p>“Sensitive skin. Expected irritation. Got none. Color’s spot on — natural, not over the top.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMDA5UL-HY_text","label":"ggMDA5UL-HY_text","default":"<p><strong>— Matt V.</strong>, 29, verified buyer</p>"}],
